msgid "Permission denied."
msgstr "Permiso denegado."

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:74
msgid "Status updated."
msgstr "Estado actualizado."

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:77
msgid "All"
msgstr "Todos"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:85
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:86
msgid "Order"
msgstr "Orden"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:87
msgid "Customer"
msgstr "Cliente"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:88
msgid "Items"
msgstr "Artículos"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:89
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Fecha"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:90
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Estado"

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:95
msgid "No withdrawal requests yet."
msgstr "Aún no hay solicitudes de retiro."

#: src/Admin/RequestsAdmin.php:120
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Guardar"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:35 src/Admin/Settings.php:36
msgid "Withdrawal"
msgstr "Retiro"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:108
msgid "Right of Withdrawal"
msgstr "Derecho de Retiro"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:109
msgid ""
"Complies with EU Directive 2023/2673 (Art. 11a): an easy withdrawal function"
" letting customers declare a full or partial withdrawal for their orders. "
"Requests are logged under WooCommerce → Withdrawal Requests."
msgstr ""
"Cumple con la Directiva de la UE 2023/2673 (Art. 11a): una función de retiro"
" fácil que permite a los clientes declarar un retiro total o parcial de sus "
"pedidos. Las solicitudes se registran en WooCommerce → Solicitudes de "
"retiro."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:112
msgid "Requests:"
msgstr "Solicitudes:"

#. translators: 1: pending, 2: accepted, 3: processed, 4: rejected
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:116
#, php-format
msgid "%1$d pending, %2$d accepted, %3$d processed, %4$d rejected"
msgstr "%1$d pendiente, %2$d aceptado, %3$d procesado, %4$d rechazado"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:123
msgid "View requests"
msgstr "Ver solicitudes"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:132
msgid "General"
msgstr "General"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:135
msgid "Withdrawal period (days)"
msgstr "Periodo de retiro (días)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:137
msgid ""
"Statutory minimum is 14 days from delivery. The window starts when the order"
" is marked completed, or at order creation if it never was."
msgstr ""
"El mínimo legal es de 14 días desde la entrega. La ventana comienza cuando "
"el pedido se marca como completado, o en el momento de la creación del "
"pedido si nunca lo estuvo."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:143
msgid "Form page"
msgstr "página de formulario"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:146
msgid "Withdrawal form page"
msgstr "Página del formulario de retiro"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:152
msgid "Select a page"
msgstr "Seleccione una página"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:155
msgid ""
"Create a page with the [withdraw_form] shortcode, then select it here so the"
" My Account button can link to it."
msgstr ""
"Cree una página con el código abreviado [withdraw_form], luego selecciónela "
"aquí para que el botón Mi cuenta pueda vincularla."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:164
msgid "Eligibility"
msgstr "Elegibilidad"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid ""
"Customers can only submit a withdrawal for orders in one of these statuses. "
"If none are checked, Completed and Processing are used."
msgstr ""
"Los clientes solo pueden enviar un retiro para pedidos en uno de estos "
"estados. Si no se marca ninguno, se utilizan Completado y Procesando."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:178
msgid "No status checked: Completed and Processing will be saved instead."
msgstr ""
"No se ha marcado ningún estado: en su lugar se guardará Completado y "
"Procesando."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:183
msgid "Emails"
msgstr "Correos electrónicos"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:186
msgid "Notification email"
msgstr "Correo electrónico de notificación"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:188
msgid ""
"Where new-request notifications are sent. Leave empty to use the site admin "
"email. The customer always gets a confirmation at their own address."
msgstr ""
"Dónde se envían las notificaciones de nuevas solicitudes. Déjelo vacío para "
"usar el correo electrónico del administrador del sitio. El cliente siempre "
"recibe una confirmación en su propia dirección."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:194
msgid "Legal texts"
msgstr "Textos legales"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:197
msgid "Form intro text"
msgstr "Texto de introducción del formulario"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:198
msgid "Shown above the order lookup step of the withdrawal form."
msgstr ""
"Se muestra encima del paso de búsqueda de pedidos del formulario de retiro."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:202
msgid "Model withdrawal text"
msgstr "Texto de retirada del modelo"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:203
msgid ""
"Shown on the form. Adapt to the statutory model withdrawal form (Annex I.B)."
msgstr ""
"Se muestra en el formulario. Adáptese al modelo reglamentario de formulario "
"de desistimiento (Anexo I.B)."

#: src/Frontend/MyAccount.php:46
msgid "Withdraw from this order"
msgstr "Desistir de este pedido"

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:84 src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:115
msgid "Security check failed. Please try again."
msgstr "El control de seguridad falló. Por favor inténtalo de nuevo."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:92 src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:122
msgid "We could not find an order with that number and email."
msgstr "No pudimos encontrar un pedido con ese número y correo electrónico."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:125
msgid "This order is no longer eligible for withdrawal."
msgstr "Este pedido ya no es elegible para retiro."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:150
msgid "Please select at least one item to withdraw from."
msgstr "Seleccione al menos un artículo del que desea retirar."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:196
msgid "This order is not in a status that can be withdrawn."
msgstr "Este pedido no se encuentra en un estado que pueda retirarse."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:206
msgid "The withdrawal period for this order has ended."
msgstr "El plazo de desistimiento de este pedido ha finalizado."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:210
msgid "A withdrawal request for this order is already being processed."
msgstr "Ya se está procesando una solicitud de retiro para este pedido."

#. translators: %s: order number
#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:229
#, php-format
msgid "Your withdrawal request for order #%s"
msgstr "Su solicitud de retiro para el pedido #%s"

#. translators: 1: order number, 2: item list, 3: reason
#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:234
#, php-format
msgid ""
"We received your withdrawal request for order #%1$s.\n"
"\n"
"Items:\n"
"%2$s\n"
"\n"
"Reason: %3$s\n"
"\n"
"We will confirm the next steps by email."
msgstr ""
"Recibimos su solicitud de retiro para el pedido n.° %1$s.\n"
"\n"
"Artículos:\n"
"%2$s\n"
"\n"
"Razón: %3$s\n"
"\n"
"Le confirmaremos los próximos pasos por correo electrónico."

#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:237 src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:255
msgid "(none given)"
msgstr "(ninguno proporcionado)"

#. translators: 1: request id, 2: order number
#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:245
#, php-format
msgid "New withdrawal request #%1$d for order #%2$s"
msgstr "Nueva solicitud de retiro #%1$d para el pedido #%2$s"

#. translators: 1: order number, 2: customer email, 3: item list, 4: reason
#: src/Service/WithdrawalService.php:251
#, php-format
msgid ""
"A customer submitted a withdrawal request.\n"
"\n"
"Order: #%1$s\n"
"Customer: %2$s\n"
"\n"
"Items:\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"Reason: %4$s"
msgstr ""
"Un cliente envió una solicitud de retiro.\n"
"\n"
"Orden: #%1$s\n"
"Cliente: %2$s\n"
"\n"
"Artículos:\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"Razón: %4$s"

#: templates/confirmation.php:17
msgid "Withdrawal request received"
msgstr "Solicitud de retiro recibida"

#. translators: 1: request id, 2: order number
#: templates/confirmation.php:22
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Your withdrawal request #%1$d for order #%2$s has been recorded. We have "
"emailed you a confirmation and will follow up with the next steps."
msgstr ""
"Se ha registrado su solicitud de retiro #%1$d para el pedido #%2$s. Le hemos"
" enviado una confirmación por correo electrónico y seguiremos con los "
"siguientes pasos."

#. translators: %s: order number
#: templates/form-items.php:23
#, php-format
msgid "Withdraw from order #%s"
msgstr "Retirar del pedido #%s"

#. translators: %s: date
#: templates/form-items.php:32
#, php-format
msgid "Withdrawal is possible until %s."
msgstr "El retiro es posible hasta el %s."

#: templates/form-items.php:47
msgid "Product"
msgstr "Producto"

#: templates/form-items.php:48
msgid "Ordered"
msgstr "Cantidad pedida"

#: templates/form-items.php:49
msgid "Withdraw quantity"
msgstr "Retirar cantidad"

#. translators: %s: product
#: templates/form-items.php:64
#, php-format
msgid "Withdraw quantity for %s"
msgstr "Retirar cantidad para %s"

#: templates/form-items.php:72
msgid "Reason (optional)"
msgstr "Razón (opcional)"

#: templates/form-items.php:83
msgid ""
"I hereby give notice that I withdraw from my contract for the selected "
"item(s)."
msgstr ""
"Por la presente notifico que desisto de mi contrato para los artículos "
"seleccionados."

#: templates/form-items.php:88
msgid "Submit withdrawal"
msgstr "Enviar retiro"

#. translators: %d: number of days
#: templates/form-lookup.php:28
#, php-format
msgid ""
"You have the right to withdraw from this contract within %d days without "
"giving any reason."
msgstr ""
"Tiene derecho a rescindir este contrato dentro de %d días sin dar ningún "
"motivo."

#: templates/form-lookup.php:42
msgid "Order number"
msgstr "Número de pedido"

#: templates/form-lookup.php:46
msgid "Billing email"
msgstr "Correo electrónico de facturación"

#: templates/form-lookup.php:50
msgid "Continue"
msgstr "Continuar"

